svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kig1665702627590.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kig1665702627590.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kig1665702627590.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kig1665702627590\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$PROFILE_VIDEO\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the video attributes for profile characters in unifields.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kig1665702627590__topic_d142613e1_d142614e1_d142615e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kig1665702627590__p_d142616e1_d142617e1_d142618e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PROFILE_VIDEO</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">VideoAttribute</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">VideoAttributeN</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>...}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kig1665702627590__section_aw1_jpv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334166e76\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kig1665702627590__p_d142622e1_d142623e1_d142624e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">VideoAttribute</var>—video attribute\n        code. To define more than one video attribute for each argument, separate them with commas\n        and enclose them in parentheses.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kig1665702627590__section_uxm_rpv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334166e87\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kig1665702627590__table_d17042e1_d17043e1_d17044e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> ny application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kig1665702627590__section_gtm_5pv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334166e133\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kig1665702627590__p_d142631e1_d142632e1_d142633e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PROFILE_VIDEO</span> sets the video\n        attributes for profile characters that appear in unifields.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kig1665702627590__section_y1h_wpv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334166e144\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$PROFILE_VIDEO</code></h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kig1665702627590__pre_k44_zpv_jwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$PROFILE_VIDEO = (UND,BOR)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kig1665702627590__p_d142637e1_d142638e1_d142639e1\">To make the active field appear with white letters on\n        a blue background, determine the color number by adding 56 (white foreground) and 1 (blue\n        background):</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kig1665702627590__pre_un4_zpv_jwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$PROFILE_VIDEO COL=57</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsj1665702873847.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Video Attributes</a><p>Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529219\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529219\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$PROFILE_VIDEO Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $PROFILE_VIDEO Set the video attributes for profile characters in unifields. $PROFILE_VIDEO { = } VideoAttribute { , VideoAttributeN , ...} Arguments VideoAttribute —video attribute code. To define more than one video attribute for each argument, separate them with commas and enclose them in parentheses. Defaults Assignment file: ny application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $PROFILE_VIDEO sets the video attributes for profile characters that appear in unifields. Example: $PROFILE_VIDEO $PROFILE_VIDEO = (UND,BOR) Copy To make the active field appear with white letters on a blue background, determine the color number by adding 56 (white foreground) and 1 (blue background): $PROFILE_VIDEO COL=57 Copy Related Links Video Attributes Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}